msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes.rst:64
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Copy Lines` option to copy the invoice lines and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Debit Note`."
msgstr ""
"Włącz opcję :guilabel:`Kopiuj wiersze`, aby skopiować wiersze faktury i "
"kliknij :guilabel:`Utwórz notę debetową`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes.rst:66
msgid ""
"In the debit note, update the :guilabel:`Product` and :guilabel:`Quantity` "
