"When registering a payment, Odoo will carry out the movement of taxes from "
"the *Cash Basis Transition Account* to the account set in "
"the :guilabel:`Definition` tab. For such movement, a tax base account will "
"be used: (`Base Imponible de Impuestos en Base a Flujo de Efectivo`) in the "
