#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:264
msgid ""
"After you have processed your `Private Key (CSD) <https://www.sat.gob.mx/"
"aplicacion/16660/genera-y-descarga-tus-archivos-a-traves-de-la-aplicacion- "
